## 🛠️ 6. How to Build Your Own Custom Notifier
If you ever want to send alerts to a Custom Database or Slack instead of Telegram, you can easily write your own notifier by implementing the `Notifier` interface in the SDK repo.

```typescript
// Inside ai-monitor-notifiers/src/SlackNotifier.ts
import { BaseNotifier, LogEvent } from '@momen124/ai-monitor-core';

export class SlackNotifier extends BaseNotifier {
    async notify(event: LogEvent): Promise<void> {
        // Your custom logic to HTTP POST the event to Slack API goes here
    }
}
```
